    {
      "id": "p001",
      "index": 1,
      "source": "Apple’s demand has catalyzed hundreds of billions in capital expenditure across the semiconductor ecosystem. The company ships over 600 million devices annually containing thousands of individual components, making it the single largest driver of precision manufacturing investment globally.",
      "source_html": null,
      "element_type": "p",
      "inline_elements": [],
      "parent_block_id": "b0363",
      "parent_block_index": 363,
      "parent_block_type": "p",
      "parent_block_markdown": "Apple’s demand has catalyzed hundreds of billions in capital expenditure across the semiconductor ecosystem. The company ships over 600 million devices annually containing thousands of individual components, making it the single largest driver of precision manufacturing investment globally.",
      "parent_block_plain_text": "Apple’s demand has catalyzed hundreds of billions in capital expenditure across the semiconductor ecosystem. The company ships over 600 million devices annually containing thousands of individual components, making it the single largest driver of precision manufacturing investment globally.",
