      "source": "TSMC: Apple volumes consume the majority of TSMC’s leading-edge capacity. TSMC’s capital expenditure has increased fivefold since 2015, reaching $29.8B in 2024 and targeting $40-42B in 2025. The company is building nine new facilities in 2025 alone.",
